title: Roast Lamb Rump & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish with Balsamic Courgette Salad
description: Tender lamb rump meets smokey-sweet chargrilled capsicum relish in this flavour-packed feast! With a fresh courgette salad and a tangy balsamic twist, it’s a vibrant, juicy number that’s big on taste and made to impress.

